data.description: Amazing opportunity to live on a quiet cul-de-sac in the quaint Roswell neighborhood of Woodfall. This nicely updated home boasts a spacious kitchen, granite counter tops, stainless appliances and extra cabinets space for plenty of storage. Living room has hardwood floors, lots of light and a wood-burning fireplace. If you like to entertain off the kitchen is a large dining room. Upstairs you will find three bedrooms including a large primary with en-suite. Both bathrooms in the home have me meticulously remodeled recently. If you crave outside space you will have plenty here. Enjoy the over-sized deck and fenced in backyard.
